{"tid":800355,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"「絕望的香港日系ACG消費市場」","createTime":"2018-08-30T19:48:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-31T18:46:40.000Z","uid":39181,"like":15,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"792aed7afeb0ae620cab89ca65c178b89093df89","tid":800355,"uid":39181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T19:48:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FHXBovtXHwE&amp;t=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DFHXBovtXHwE%26t%3D&d=072fkaJ4UVi5TGaQXQwwkOI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=a2399b68\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FHXBovtXHwE&amp;t=</a><br />\n我覺得條片講得幾有道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n入面講到香港既日系ACG消費市場因為缺乏生產者，香港好少代理商得分銷商，我地啲周邊生產好多都係台灣黎整，但台灣有時要迎合佢地自己既情況而無辦法畀到啲貨香港，搞到香港人覺得自己地方啲周邊好少<br />\n<br />\n跟住當啲消費者就算有足夠既消費慾，但佢地搵唔到可以消費既地方唯有將依啲錢用晒飛去日本消費或者代購身上，結果香港既日系ACG消費市場做唔到一個經濟生活循環，一路頹落去<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/31/025331_be39d6e3949058e712b7cc0700c28af2.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F31%2F025331_be39d6e3949058e712b7cc0700c28af2.JPG&h=a8f0c0f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後仲講到香港冇一個專門既ACG平台，冇得好似b站啲up主咁提供啲片賣下廣告、提供資訊咁<br />\n有得畀啲客群見識多啲同提升消費慾<br />\n另外香港就算有好似連登咁大型既論壇，但動漫台都好少搬運啲動漫資訊得啲9upper，吸引唔到其他人上黎，結果香港因為無一個專門既ACG平台 做唔到聚眾效應<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n諗起隔離個post黎明卿會然有句野講得幾啱「bilibili大會然其實都唔算正版,<br />\n因為人地買黎係比中國播,唔係比中國以外既地方睇」<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正因為香港日系ACG消費市場太多野配套不足，啲錢飛走晒周圍，無辦法流向本地市場只會愈黎愈頹<br />\n而人氣方面因為冇合適平台，人流唯有流晒去貼吧、巴哈、k島個啲地方，個度又大把資訊、大把人做動畫分析講野又好笑，結果畀人吸引左連文化都依附左人地<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最終結果香港日系ACG消費市場收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8e1a00c3fda195ef76f70b649b2668439940894","tid":800355,"uid":35667,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T19:50:27.000Z","msg":"黎明又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fd6f712c380d445b0c5cb386435c3f12afab947","tid":800355,"uid":8307,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T20:06:14.000Z","msg":"香港本身人少<br />\n真沉迷acg既更少<br />\n有商家捨得投資實好dum本 <br />\n搞左之後持續發展都難撐落去<br />\n<br />\n日本仔自己搞既sell動畫去海外既網<br />\nDaisuki都執柒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7f02ccac9bc2263b021a4dad28aa58ad18bdf18","tid":800355,"uid":22692,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T20:12:12.000Z","msg":"有咩好發展<br />\n依家要咩貨都有得訂"},{"pid":"cdde206656f1c72bca6c0fbd20cb36a6dd2b2fc8","tid":800355,"uid":150609,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T20:24:39.000Z","msg":"政府冇為我地動漫迷做過野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1936afa16628d5c685022830fa7cff1e92992423","tid":800355,"uid":44073,"like":4,"dislike":8,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T21:41:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e7d8f1e27594ff2e21c3a9e4a23c20c9ddf7e290","tid":800355,"uid":1085,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T22:03:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"41bdc0b4e9c6d833d66c7914406b5896cb6f2124","tid":800355,"uid":44073,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T22:06:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f10cc9a5ef282a9c0b660e4a6edef78f8ea8b0b5","tid":800355,"uid":65155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T22:16:26.000Z","msg":"動漫台打多兩隻字又話too long didnt rrad"},{"pid":"02721b77f8a7c53a593b91ca672fd009a30ba520","tid":800355,"uid":44073,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T22:21:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3bfd16b3981060a036b9351fa219ab0fc0d1b4fe","tid":800355,"uid":44073,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T22:28:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6d2fff5e9e6d9511e398804d026620b6a354f184","ti